  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 947c76105d7454747a8fc8874cd8bff8, type: 3}
  m_Name: Bad end
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrationLines
  lines:
  - She drops her swords, panting heavily as her head hangs low.
  - "\u201C...*pant*...*pant*...Damn you\u2026You and your words\u2026"
  - "You and your lies\u2026"
  - "I hope that when your time comes, you rot in hell\u2026"
  - "I will never forgive the likes of you\u2026"
  - "not ever.\u201D"
  - 'I look at her. '
  - Her figure trembles slightly, as though she is trying to hold back her tears.
  - She eventually fades away.
  - Mission accomplished.
  - "But it doesn\u2019t feel like that."
  line: "But it doesn\u2019t feel like that."
